Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.25,0:01:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边有三个空位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's room for three right there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我们买票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for getting us tickets
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看盛大的比赛  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the big game, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.68,0:01:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speaking of
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我们欠你的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's what we owe ya
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a problem, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.10,0:01:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了  还记得我为什么邀请你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, you do remember why I invited you?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absolutely
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来支持珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to back Pearl up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时候做你编的蟹堡王秘密啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when she does the secret Krusty Krab cheer you wrote
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这边这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how many people are here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费打广告最划算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't beat free advertisin'
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.46,0:01:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从小就梦想着要做一个啦啦队员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a little sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's been my dream to be a cheerleader
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从两秒钟前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever since two seconds ago
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就梦想着要找到厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's been my dream to find a toilet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,憋住小便最最差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holding it is the worst
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星膀胱会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's bladder's gonna burst
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你进厕所前最好先别炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not before you get to the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这操做得好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's good stuff, boy-o, good stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还是等打广告再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But save it for the advertisement
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这附近肯定有厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be a bathroom around here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算能舒坦地解手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet release
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可是解说间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the announcer's booth
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就宣布我要解手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm announcing that I have to tinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(924,920)}解 说
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转下身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一直看  我尿不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't go if you're watching
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  比赛就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, the game's about to start
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦队员上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here come the cheerleaders
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍肯定等不及要做我编的啦啦操了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet Pearl can't wait to do my cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rah-rah-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖女儿珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearly-girl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好帮老爸促销蟹黄堡了没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to help Daddy sell some patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rah-rah-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一飞冲天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sis-boom-bah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她好像没听到  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think she heard you, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来引起她的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get her attention
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先鱼们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlefish
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛就要开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the game is about to begin
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so let's get ready
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为我们的裤头村藤壶队加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to cheer for our own Bikini Bottom Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便给我排空的膀胱加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And cheer for my empty bladder
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么还不走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别碰话筒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off the mic
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,触地得分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touchdown
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可开了个坏头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is not a good start
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这比赛要打很久的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a long game, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有得是时间可以扳回一城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plenty of time for a comeback
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这运气可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is some bad luck
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He fell down
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个擒杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a sack
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(990,920)}袋
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没照着他们的意愿走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That didn't go their way
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都想吃蝴蝶脆饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could go for a pretzel
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rah-rah-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一飞冲天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sis-boom-bah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rah-rah-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一飞冲天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sis-boom-bah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  比赛进展很不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick, this game is going so poorly
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都想不到还能怎么形容不顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of ways to say "it's going poorly"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那了得起怎么样  帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about "badtastic," Perch?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主队的战况极度了得起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going extremely badtastic for the home team
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们只落后一分简直是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle they're only down by one point
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,姐妹们  听好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, girls, listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们队还有机会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our team can still win
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.24,0:05:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但还需要有特别的东西来激励他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but they need something special to get them motivated
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They need
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ultimate cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们做终极啦啦操从来就没成功过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've never successfully done the ultimate cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上次我们做了  害贝姬现在都没康复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Becky still hasn't recovered
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the last time we tried it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能行的  米齐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do it, Mitzy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一定行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know we can
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了团队  不做也得做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to, for the team
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrack 'em up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stack 'em up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高高叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pile 'em to the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,决一死战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do or die
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy moly, we did it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家目光都聚焦在啦啦队员身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's eyes are on the cheerleaders
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在正好可以来做我的蟹堡王啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now's the perfect time for me Krusty Krab cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,执行蟹黄堡宣传行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Commence Operation Patty Plug
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡儿真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties, taste so great
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡儿买八个才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties, you must buy eight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,266)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直不可思议  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但有一个啦啦队员似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but a cheerleader appears
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被橄榄球堵住了呼吸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to have the football stuck in her blowhole
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且比赛还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the play is still going
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个触地得那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's one of those touchy-downy things
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even better
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是胜利的触地得那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was the winning touchy-downy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是  触地得分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, touchdown
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.16,0:06:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barn-a-cles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:45.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,432)}高中
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们昨晚看比赛看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We saw you at the game last night
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给我尾鳍签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sign my tail fin?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在尽我的一份力而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just doing my part, I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(888,866)}珍珍
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over for you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鳕鱼教练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Coach Cod
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚的事情很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about last night
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以后会尽量远离球场的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try to stay off the field in the future
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远离吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay off?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  我要你上球场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I need you on the field
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,橄榄球队有你这么彪悍的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a bruiser like you on the football team
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定可以夺冠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we could win the championship
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我热爱参加啦啦队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I love being on the Cheer Squad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道能不能离开队友们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I could leave them
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上课要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm late for class
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd I tell ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彪悍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bruiser
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你能决定加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad you decided to join us
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴好头盔上场去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab a helmet and get out there on the field
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,训练就快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Practice is just starting
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you say so
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给我见识一下你的本领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you show me what you've got?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好从基本功开始练起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'd better start with the basics
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打橄榄球用不着蹦蹦跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no prancing in football
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You run
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  跑得也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, that's enough running
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看你接球的水平如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see how you are at catching the ball
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是向四分卫示意自己可以接球了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is signaling to the quarterback that you're open
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好有个啦啦操能引起他的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have the perfect cheer to get his attention
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个橄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,F-O-O
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个榄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,T-B-A
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来球  比赛就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,L-L is the game we play
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,传给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm open
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以接到球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm O-P-E-N, open
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.99,0:08:31.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:31.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改练阻截试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try some tackling instead
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,队友们  撞过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, team, show me some hits
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狠狠撞疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring the pain
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十码线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten-yard line
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停船场线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Parking lot line
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,End of the line
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1060,920)}线
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好那底下有辆救护车垫着做缓冲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing this ambulance was there to break my fall
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  训练结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, practice is over
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.57,0:09:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家来参加我们的啦啦队员面试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for coming to our cheerleader auditions
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们肩负上一任队员珍珍的重任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got some whale-sized shoes to fill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1392,920)}鞋
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以来看看你们有什么本领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so let's see what you've got
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,悲观失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doom and Gloom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前景灰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Black and Grey
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们今天害对手玩完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you crush your foes today
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还挺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was very
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,peppy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, next
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是鱿鱼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidina Star
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正在做一部纪录片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm making a documentary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主题是加入啦啦队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about joining the cheer squad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先绑好我的第一人称头戴式摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just need to strap on my POV camera
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能开始表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I start my routine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会等纪录片发行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we'll wait for the movie to come out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫弗雷德丽卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is Frederica
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.88,0:10:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是来为你们加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I came here to cheer you on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的女儿好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my girl
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来大打特打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We came here to fight
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚在橄榄球场  保证把你们打趴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will kick your booties
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the football field tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你们看到我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you see us coming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会求安全想自卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For your safety you will beg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你们最多只会听到我们喊出小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the only thing you'll hear from us is watch out for
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弗雷德丽卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Frederica?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕  弗雷德老表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Cousin Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.17,0:10:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.04,0:10:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你  弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help you, Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该会耗上好一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This could take awhile
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有没有谁可以正常做啦啦操的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who can actually do a normal cheer?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边这位会你们所有的啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got someone who knows all your cheers
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们机会来了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is our chance, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一旦加入了啦啦队  就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once you make the squad, you can
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在一大群观众面前表演我的啦啦操了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get my cheer in front of the masses
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rah-rah-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rah-rah-rah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没断腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he didn't break his leg
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还好轻盈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he's so light
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用来到处抛还特别理想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a dream to throw around
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That does it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入啦啦队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the squad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一次正式比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My first official game
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回到又一场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back to another
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.31,0:11:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刺激的藤壶队橄榄球之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,exciting evening of Barnacles Football
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你们今晚的解说员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be your announcer tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为厕所是我先到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I made it to the bathroom first
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Occupied
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Occupied?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,球来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ball?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍有那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl has the thingy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是其他人想要那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but these other guys want the thingy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别被他们抢了那玩意  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let them have the thingy, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home run
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.86,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 棒球 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱橄榄球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love football
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,触地得分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touchdown
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Game over
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藤壶队获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles win
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme a P
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一个㐱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme an E
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给我来一个珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme an A-R-L
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拼起来是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it spell?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  先别提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still adding it up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还能算出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I coulda done it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么名堂  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you playin' at, boy-o?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没做我编的蟹堡王啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't do my Krusty Krab cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下场比赛一定会做的  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do it next game, I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好给我做出来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See that you do, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See that you do
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.91,0:14:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So cool
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我的壳签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sign my shell?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就爱你那态度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love the attitude
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你变了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've really changed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话  我当然变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no duh I've changed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是全校史上最厉害的橄榄球员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the greatest football player
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this school has ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hike
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我们的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's our girl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她要是不行  我会呕吐狂喷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If she can't do it, I'll totally hurl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我有点担心今晚的锦标赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm worried about tonight's Championship Game
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  教练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Coach
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一场  我保证能再赢一场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another game, another win
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这个视频片段  拍的是我们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this footage of our opponents
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纽开普市少年犯队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The New Kelp City Delinquents
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.00,0:15:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全队留级了几十年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Their entire team
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been held back in school for decades
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:07.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,692)}纽开普市高中
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些家伙坏透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These guys are bad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从鱼鳃坏到了尾鳍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean from their gills to their tail fins
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以也许我们还是弃赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So maybe we should just forfeit
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们看着猛  只是因为没遇到我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They only look tough 'cause they haven't met me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请裤头村藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your Bikini Bottom Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及前来以工代监的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here on a work release program
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纽开普市少年犯队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The New Kelp City Delinquents
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  队友们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, team
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常到这时候我会讲些鼓舞士气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Normally I'd give a pep talk right now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我觉得现在更适合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I think this time would be better spent
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们的至亲至爱告别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,saying goodbye to your loved ones
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, hands in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  我还听说少年犯队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, and I heard the Delinquents
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在场上布了水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may have mined the field
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你们比赛小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so just be careful out there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  就几个水雷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys, it's just a few mines
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起给他们见识下我们藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's show 'em what Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么本领
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are made of?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  藤壶队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那头鲸鱼是我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That whale's me daughter
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场比赛都没输过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and she's never lost a game
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边那位是我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's my boy out there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场比赛也没输过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he's never lost a game either
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么  他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, him?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他上高中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in high school?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What year is he?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十年刑期的第五年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five years into a ten-year stretch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现良好的话  第八年可能就毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He might graduate in eight with good behavior
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我女儿珍珍肯定能打得他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, me Pearly-Girl is gonna make him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望自己能按时毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wish he had graduated on time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要打赌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna bet?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是藤壶队赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the Barnacles win
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就得给我五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you gotta give me five bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要是输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if they lose?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是藤壶队会输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the Barnacles were to lose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费蟹黄堡给大家送出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free Krabby Patties for all of youse
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赌就赌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take that bet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what're you doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那赌注可比五块钱贵多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's worth a whole lot more than five bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能怎么输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could we lose?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们队里有珍珍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got Pearl on our side
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  藤壶呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Barnacle Heads
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又到了一场精彩刺激的保龄球之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's another exciting night of bowling ball
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,球一个大脚踢出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's the big kick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来他找到了他们进攻方的漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like he found a hole in their offense
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍要把球踢回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl's gonna return the kick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她像赛马一样冲了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's off like a racehorse
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.54,0:18:34.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在又像赛马一样被压扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:34.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now she's being crushed like a racehorse
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算是粉身碎骨也拦不住珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl's not gonna let all her crushed bones stop her
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可能是有一点自负了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might have been a little overconfident
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们还能扳回一城  对吧队友们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we can still turn it around, right, team?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.09,0:19:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  场上的藤壶队队员只剩珍珍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Folks, Pearl is the only Barnacle left on the field
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他们打算让她继续比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but they're going to let her play on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck to ya
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们会把我搞死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These guys are gonna kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你看着很紧张的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pearl, you look nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.86,0:19:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟你分享一个特别的啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna share a special cheer with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我奶奶教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My grandma taught it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每当日子难熬  境况不畅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:46.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When days are tough and things go bad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶会帮你不再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grandmas help you not feel sad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.00,0:19:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假如奶奶不在  你依然烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If Gran's not here and you're still blue
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了做自己就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,remember to just be you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做自己就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just be me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma is right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢做一个橄榄球星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I liked being a football star
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我热爱做一名啦啦队员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I love being a cheerleader
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一飞冲天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sis-boom-bah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-R-U
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个堡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-T-Y
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来个王  正正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K-R-A-B, my-oh-my
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王营业到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is open late
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买蟹黄堡  味道赞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So buy some patties, they taste great
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在做我编的啦啦操
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's doing me cheer
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你什么都没干  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for nothin', SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有薯条和汽水饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got fries and sody drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one more thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chum Bucket stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.90,0:21:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射门得分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goooooal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:01.15,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 足球 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,158)}裤头村高中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(838,378)}主队           第{\fnArial}4{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}节         客队
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Game over
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少年犯队获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Delinquents win
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么重要的比赛  我竟然输了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I lost the big game
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别对自己那么苛刻  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, don't be too hard on yourself, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我们对战少年犯队的最高分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the best score
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've ever had against the Delinquents
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们明年一定能战胜他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely get 'em next year
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  教练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Coach
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我明年不会回来参赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I won't be coming back next year
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚的事让我想起了我的第一爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight helped me remember my first love
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啦啦队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cheerleading
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况  啦啦队还缺一个队员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think there's an opening on the squad
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.57,0:21:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是学生就不可以参加啦啦队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't be a cheerleader if you're not a student
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.33,0:21:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别做啦啦操了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop cheering
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你不要把它从我身边夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't take this away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厕所归你了  哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bathroom is yours, my man
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Game over
